<div class="flex flex-col h-screen">
    <div class="flex">
        {{> aside }}
        <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto bg-slate-50">
            {{> admin/navbar hidden_search="hidden" title="User Support" content="Let us help you with our detailed"}}
            <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col py-2 px-4">
                <div class="flex bg-gray-50">
                    <div class="w-2/3 pl-0 pr-8">
                        <div id="aside" class="flex w-full">
                            <div class="rounded-tl-2xl border-black border-[2px] border-l-[2px] border-r-[1px] bg-black text-[#f3d2c3] w-full py-2 px-4 text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer text-center"
                                data-section="dashboard-help">Dashboard</div>
                            <div class="border-black border-y-[2px] border-x-[1px] w-full py-2 px-4 text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer text-center"
                                data-section="users-help">Users</div>
                            <div class="border-black border-y-[2px] border-x-[1px] w-full py-2 px-4 text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer text-center"
                                data-section="products-help">Products</div>
                            <div class="border-black border-y-[2px] border-x-[1px] w-full py-2 px-4 text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer text-center"
                                data-section="orders-help">Orders</div>
                            <div class="rounded-tr-2xl border-black border-y-[2px] border-r-[2px] border-l-[1px] w-full py-2 px-4 text-lg font-semibold cursor-pointer text-center"
                                data-section="profile-help">Profile</div>
                        </div>

                        <div id="dashboard-help" class="border-white rounded-b-2xl bg-white shadow-lg p-6">
                            <p class="text-justify">On this page, administrators have access to a detailed and
                                comprehensive overview of essential statistics related to the application, encompassing
                                critical data on users, products, and orders. These statistics are thoughtfully designed
                                to provide a clear understanding of key performance metrics and usage patterns. Detailed
                                information is presented in multiple formats, including textual data for quick insights
                                and visual representations such as pie charts, bar graphs, and line charts, enabling
                                deeper analysis of trends, distributions, and relationships among data points.
                                Customizable filters and sorting options allow administrators to focus on specific
                                aspects of the data most relevant to their needs. The primary purpose of this page is to
                                offer an all-encompassing yet insightful perspective on the application's key entities,
                                empowering administrators to make data-driven decisions, identify opportunities or
                                issues, and effectively manage and optimize the sales platform for better outcomes.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div id="users-help" class="bg-white rounded-b-2xl shadow-lg p-6 hidden">
                            <p class="text-justify">This page is designed to assist administrators in efficiently
                                managing user information, ensuring seamless oversight and control over all registered
                                accounts. It offers a set of tools that enable administrators to view and edit personal
                                details, such as names, emails, usernames, and other profile attributes. A prominently
                                positioned search bar in the header facilitates quick searches by username or email,
                                helping administrators locate specific accounts effortlessly, even with extensive
                                datasets. Administrators can update user details to maintain accuracy or delete inactive
                                or redundant accounts. The interface is user-friendly, ensuring that even complex tasks
                                are intuitive. This page streamlines the user management process while upholding high
                                standards of security and data integrity, making it essential for administrators to
                                manage, optimize, and scale the platform effectively while ensuring a positive user
                                experience.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div id="products-help" class="bg-white rounded-b-2xl shadow-lg p-6 hidden">
                            <p class="text-justify">This page provides administrators with powerful tools to manage
                                detailed product information, ensuring the catalog remains accurate, well-organized, and
                                up-to-date. A search bar in the header enables administrators to quickly locate products
                                by titles, brands, categories, or other attributes, simplifying navigation through
                                extensive inventories. Administrators can add new products, update existing ones, or
                                delete discontinued or unavailable items. Additionally, this page offers access to
                                customer reviews and feedback, providing insights into customer preferences,
                                satisfaction levels, and trends. By analyzing these reviews, administrators can identify
                                areas for improvement, address issues, and enhance customer satisfaction. This page is
                                key to effective product management, maintaining quality, consistency, and reliability
                                while fostering continuous improvement in service delivery.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div id="orders-help" class="bg-white rounded-b-2xl shadow-lg p-6 hidden">
                            <p class="text-justify">This page provides administrators with a centralized platform to
                                manage all orders that users have completed payment for, ensuring efficient and accurate
                                processing. A search bar in the header allows for quick searches by username, making it
                                easy to locate specific orders, even in large transaction datasets. Administrators can
                                view a comprehensive list of orders, including details such as order IDs, product
                                descriptions, quantities, and payment statuses, enabling them to prepare and organize
                                orders effectively. This functionality supports timely and accurate delivery, allowing
                                admins to prioritize tasks and streamline operations. By offering a clear overview and
                                accessible tools, this page enhances order management workflows and ensures customers
                                receive their purchases promptly and without errors, contributing to a better overall
                                service experience.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div id="profile-help" class="bg-white rounded-b-2xl shadow-lg p-6 hidden">
                            <p class="text-justify">This page provides administrators with an intuitive, user-friendly
                                platform for efficiently managing their personal information, ensuring a seamless and
                                organized experience. It allows administrators to view, edit, and update personal
                                details in a structured manner, maintaining accuracy and efficiency. One key feature is
                                the ability to update profile pictures by uploading a new image directly from their
                                device, ensuring profiles remain professional and personalized. Additional features
                                include sections for editing contact information, usernames, and other relevant details,
                                making navigation straightforward, even for those with minimal technical expertise. The
                                interface is clean and visually appealing, improving usability. By centralizing personal
                                information management, this page helps administrators keep profiles accurate and
                                up-to-date. The seamless upload functionality and efficient design save time, enabling
                                administrators to focus on higher-priority tasks. Overall, this page enhances
                                efficiency, personalization, and user experience, empowering administrators to perform
                                their roles effectively.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-1/3 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-4">
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <img src="/system_images/Help.gif" alt="Help assistance"
                                class="rounded-xl shadow-lg h-96 object-cover">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
    <div>
        {{> footer }}
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    const asideItems = document.querySelectorAll('#aside div');
    const helpSections = document.querySelectorAll('[id$="-help"]');

    asideItems.forEach(item => {
        item.addEventListener('click', () => {
            helpSections.forEach(section => section.classList.add('hidden'));
            asideItems.forEach(asideItem => asideItem.classList.remove('bg-black', 'text-[#f3d2c3]'));
            item.classList.add('bg-black', 'text-[#f3d2c3]');
            const sectionId = item.getAttribute('data-section');
            document.getElementById(sectionId).classList.remove('hidden');
        });
    });
</script>